{"tid":1499644,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過m到去睇婦科？同埋有無介紹？","createTime":"2019-08-23T19:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T06:06:40.000Z","uid":133586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c2ba09623242bd1db1b6db0f9b1678fae2cd2c","tid":1499644,"uid":133586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:16:40.000Z","msg":"早兩日發現，應該係叫小陰唇入面，生左粒野...<br />\n紅紅腫腫，小便會痛...<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日都返工同埋約左人，所以無時間睇醫生，仲要唔知應該去邊度睇，因為咁多年都淨係識去普通診所睇醫生，仲要睇開嘅都係男醫生...<br />\n<br />\n但係...今日啱啱m到...<br />\nm到緊就算我搵到醫生睇，都唔知點俾佢睇...<br />\n<br />\n救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d62464add58b808bef0e1e8c99399599bc55ee","tid":1499644,"uid":128204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:41:29.000Z","msg":"啲醫生咩都睇慣啦 怕乜"},{"pid":"513514a1f31a74b6fcc296aa1a23e06c02d732b1","tid":1499644,"uid":3727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T20:20:42.000Z","msg":"塞棉條去睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部都係血應該好難睇得清"},{"pid":"39df5deaef15e66d25c705f63f22c7fe9f09fbbb","tid":1499644,"uid":133586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"513514a1f31a74b6fcc296aa1a23e06c02d732b1","tid":1499644,"uid":3727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T20:20:42.000Z","msg":"塞棉條去睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji